<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c4">[السَّعير]</span>: حَرُّ النار،<span class="c5"> قال الله تعالى:</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَفَرِيقٌ فِي السَّعِيرِ <span class="c2">«٣»</span>.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
